title: MoS Jitin Prasada visits Romania for 19th India-Romania Joint Committee for Economic Cooperation meeting
description:
New Delhi [India], November 3 (ANI): Minister of State for Commerce and Industry Jitin Prasada is on an official visit to Bucharest at the invitation of the Government of Romania to attend the 19th meeting of the Joint Committee for Economic Cooperation (JCEC) between India and Romania.
